    • Method Detail

      • buildViewEpisodeIntent

        public static Intent buildViewEpisodeIntent​(int showTvdbId,
                                            int episodeTvdbId)
        Builds an implicit Intent to view an episode in SeriesGuide. Make sure to check with Intent.resolveActivity(android.content.pm.PackageManager) if SeriesGuide (or another app capable of handling this intent) is available.
        Parameters:
        showTvdbId - If valid and the episode does not exist, the user will be asked if the show should be added to SeriesGuide.

      • buildViewShowIntent

        public static Intent buildViewShowIntent​(int showTvdbId)
        Builds an implicit Intent to view a show in SeriesGuide. Make sure to check with Intent.resolveActivity(android.content.pm.PackageManager) if SeriesGuide (or another app capable of handling this intent) is available.

        If the show is not added to SeriesGuide, the user will be asked if it should be.
